  "Signed in to HenryCo.": {"fr":"Connecté à HenryCo.","es":"Sesión iniciada en HenryCo.","pt":"Sessão iniciada na HenryCo.","ar":"تم تسجيل الدخول إلى HenryCo.","de":"Bei HenryCo angemeldet.","it":"Accesso effettuato a HenryCo.","zh":"已登录 HenryCo。","hi":"HenryCo में साइन इन किया गया।","ig":"Abanyela na HenryCo.","yo":"Wọlé sí HenryCo.","ha":"An shiga HenryCo."},
  "Skip to main content": {"fr":"Aller au contenu principal","es":"Saltar al contenido principal","pt":"Saltar para o conteúdo principal","ar":"الانتقال إلى المحتوى الرئيسي","de":"Zum Hauptinhalt springen","it":"Vai al contenuto principale","zh":"跳转到主要内容","hi":"मुख्य सामग्री पर जाएँ","ig":"Wụga na ọdịnaya bụ isi","yo":"Fò sí àkóónú àkọ́kọ́","ha":"Tsallake zuwa babban abun ciki"},
